    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is gone. the company, the equity, the savings... all of it. i just lost the last of the bridge funding today. i cant even think about going back to my parents or my wife. they saw me as this success story and now i'm just a guy with a mountain of debt and nothing to show for it. the shame is actually physically painful. i feel like i'm just a burden to everyone i know now.",
