    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "professional counseling? i dont need a lawyer or a counselor, i need the feeling of being a total failure to stop. every time i look at them, i just feel like i'm lying to them by even being alive when i've failed so badly. it feels like there's no way to actually fix the way people see me. the debt is just... it's permanent. the disgrace is permanent. it feels like the only way to actually stop the weight of it is to just not be here anymore.",
